---
- Time-series efficiency
- TimescaleDB hypertables with automatic partitioning by timestamp
---
- Multi-timeframe analysis
- Continuous Aggregates auto-generate 2h, 4h, 12h, 1d, 3d, 1w, 1m views
---
- Automated indicator computation
- Celery workers calculate 15+ technical signals after every data ingestion
---
