## 8. Task Schedule Summary

```
gantt
    title Recurring Task Schedule (rolling 1-hour window)
    dateFormat HH:mm
    axisFormat %H:%M

    section Every Hour
    CcxtInitTask (asset refresh + OHLCV fetch) :active, 00:00, 60m

    section Every 30 min
    CoingeckoTask (market data snapshot)       :active, 00:00, 30m
    CoingeckoTask (market data snapshot)       :active, 00:30, 30m

    section Triggered (event-driven)
    CalcIndicatorsTask (after each OHLCV write) :crit, 00:05, 20m

    section Weekly
    DbCleanupTask (prune old indicators)        :done, 00:00, 10m

```

{% table %}
- Task
- Trigger
- Description
---
- `CcxtInitTask`
- Every 1 hour
- Refresh asset universe, fetch latest 1h OHLCV from all 5 exchanges
---
- `AssetListingTask`
- Chained from CcxtInitTask
- Sync full market listings from 8 exchanges + CoinGecko
---
- `ExchangeTask` (×5)
- Parallel group after listing
- Per-exchange OHLCV fetch and DB write
---
- `CalcIndicatorsTask`
- Event-driven (after OHLCV insert)
- Compute all 15+ indicators for updated assets across all 8 timeframes
---
- `CoingeckoTask`
- Every 30 minutes
- Fetch top-2000 coins market data, compute ATH proximity flags
---
- `DbCleanupTask`
- Weekly
- Delete stale indicator rows, keep only latest per asset/timeframe bucket
{% /table %}

